Chevy Silverado 1500 2019 - 2026<\/strong>","highlight_style":"none","enable_highlight_text_color":true,"heading_size":"h1","heading_color":"#5683c2"}},"text_CfcJd4":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Stop worrying about weight limits and start adventuring with confidence. <strong>Offroad Industries (ORI)<\/strong> offers the most comprehensive, Federally Approved GVM (Gross Vehicle Mass) upgrades for the Chevy Silverado 1500 (LTZ, Trail Boss, and ZR2). <\/p><p>By bundling the <strong>ORI GVM Packages & <\/strong> <strong>GCM testing<\/strong> and the combination of <strong>LS16 certification<\/strong>, you are offering a legal \"Super-Truck\" status. The <strong>LS16 code<\/strong> is the secret sauce here: it’s the specific modification code for <strong>Gross Combination Mass Re-rating<\/strong>, ensuring the truck, the gear, and the massive 4.5T trailer are all <\/p><p>100% legal together for either PRE or Post Rego<\/p><p>Whether you’re a weekend explorer, a tradie with a heavy load, or a serious tourer towing a 4.5T caravan, our staged packages transform your truck’s legality, safety, and performance.<\/p><p>*<strong>Please note that some workshops may apply additional discretionary administration fees to the quoted installation and engineering price. Additionally, all Post-Registration GVM upgrades will incur additional local fees. Shipping is not included in the price.<\/strong><\/p>"}}},"block_order":["heading_XhCLHT","text_CfcJd4"],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.name","settings":{"container":"container","color_schema":"","text_alignment":"left","padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":0,"show_section_divider":false,"divider_width":"container","custom_id":"","custom_class":"","animations":"inherit"}},"rich_text_PtmRiF":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_mpxUJy":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"ORI GVM & GCM PACKAGES","highlight_style":"underline","enable_highlight_text_color":true,"heading_size":"h1","heading_color":"#5683c2"}}},"block_order":["heading_mpxUJy"],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.name","settings":{"container":"container","color_schema":"","text_alignment":"left","padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":0,"show_section_divider":false,"divider_width":"container","custom_id":"gvmpackages","custom_class":"","animations":"inherit"}},"image_with_text_WcaAiR":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"subheading_JVKNjL":{"type":"subheading","settings":{"subheading":"Stage 1: $11,500* - Installed & Engineered"}},"heading_f9G7kD":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"<strong>Stage 1: The Weekender Family Getaway (3650kg GVM + GCM 8150kg)<\/strong>","highlight_style":"none","enable_highlight_text_color":false,"heading_size":"h2"}},"text_fRRw7g":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><em>The perfect entry point for those needing a legal payload boost without a major lift.<\/em><\/p><ul><li><strong>GVM Increase:<\/strong> Up to 3650kg (approx. 1077kg payload).<\/li><li><strong>Key Features:<\/strong> Fox 2.5 Performance Series shocks and ORI 200kg heavy-duty leaf packs matched with heavy duty BDS control arms.<\/li><li><strong>Best For:<\/strong> Daily drivers and light towing where you need to clear the \"one-tonne\" mark for tax purposes (ATO compliance) or carry extra tools\/gear legally.<\/li><li><strong>Benefit:<\/strong> Maintains a lifted stance with premium USA-made shocks,  while significantly improving stability under load without the need of purchasing load rated wheels.<\/li><li><strong>Part Number:<\/strong> CHV-1500-Stage1-GVM<\/li><\/ul>"}}},"block_order":["subheading_JVKNjL","heading_f9G7kD","text_fRRw7g"],"name":"t:sections.image-with-text.presets.name","settings":{"container":"container","color_schema":"","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/GVM_CHEVY-1500---20260429stage-1-_-3650-GVM-CHEVY-1500.png","image_width":"50%","image_position":"left","vertical_alignment":"center","column_gap":"medium","row_gap":"medium","padding_left":0,"padding_right":0,"align_content_container":"none","mobile_padding_left":15,"mobile_padding_right":15,"padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":40,"padding_top_mobile":60,"padding_bottom_mobile":60,"show_section_divider":false,"divider_width":"container","custom_id":"","custom_class":"","animations":"inherit"}},"image_with_text_pR9RXR":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"subheading_nNBqbG":{"type":"subheading","settings":{"subheading":"Stage 2: $7,800* - Installed & Engineered"}},"heading_dHpa9y":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"<strong>Stage 2:  ZR2 Only Performance Level-Up (3650kg GVM + GCM up to 7850Kg)<\/strong>","highlight_style":"none","enable_highlight_text_color":false,"heading_size":"h2"}},"text_eiTTm6":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><em>Increased strength without the cost of replacing all your suspension + legal one tonne payload.<\/em><\/p><ul><li><strong>GVM Increase:<\/strong> 3650kg.<\/li><li><strong>Key Features:<\/strong> Adds <strong>BDS Upper Control Arms<\/strong> and a leveling kit (or 2\" lift options) retains the factory Multimatic Suspension<\/li><li><strong>Best For:<\/strong> Chevy Silverado ZR2 owners only need to clear the \"one-tonne\" mark for tax purposes (ATO compliance) or carry extra tools\/gear legally.<\/li><li><strong>Benefit:<\/strong> Enhanced front-end strength and wheel travel, ideal for ZR2 owner who retain the OEM suspension yet get 1 tonne payload.<\/li><li><strong>Part Number:<\/strong> CHV-1500-Stage2-GVM<\/li><\/ul><p><\/p>"}}},"block_order":["subheading_nNBqbG","heading_dHpa9y","text_eiTTm6"],"name":"t:sections.image-with-text.presets.name","settings":{"container":"container","color_schema":"","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/GVM_CHEVY-1500---20260429stage-2-_-3650-GVM-CHEVY-1500.png","image_width":"50%","image_position":"right","vertical_alignment":"center","column_gap":"medium","row_gap":"medium","padding_left":0,"padding_right":0,"align_content_container":"none","mobile_padding_left":15,"mobile_padding_right":15,"padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":40,"padding_top_mobile":60,"padding_bottom_mobile":60,"show_section_divider":false,"divider_width":"container","custom_id":"","custom_class":"","animations":"inherit"}},"image_with_text_M8ykcj":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"subheading_p3JeNT":{"type":"subheading","settings":{"subheading":"Stage 3: $15,999* - Installed & Engineered"}},"heading_KMefdY":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"<strong>Stage 3: The Ultimate Tourer (3850kg GVM + GCM up to 8350kg)<\/strong>","highlight_style":"none","enable_highlight_text_color":false,"heading_size":"h2"}},"text_aVwiWh":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><em>Engineered for the ultimate suspension, <\/em><\/p><ul><li><strong>GVM Increase:<\/strong> 3850kg (approx. 1272kg payload). GCM Increase 8050 KG ZR2 or 8350 LTZ<\/li><li><strong>Key Features:<\/strong> Premium <strong>Fox 2.5 DSC (Dual Speed Compression)<\/strong> adjustable shocks.<\/li><li><strong>Best For:<\/strong> Heavy-duty touring. If you have a bull bar, and a heavy tow ball weight from a large caravan, this is your sweet spot without having to upgrade your wheel and tyre package.<\/li><li><strong>Benefit:<\/strong> The DSC adjustability allows you to \"dial in\" your ride—stiffen it for the highway and soften it for the tracks at the turn of a knob. Fox’s premium shocks setup for the Chevy Silverado 1500.<\/li><li><strong>Part Number: <\/strong>CHV-1500-Stage3-GVM<br\/><br\/><\/li><\/ul>"}}},"block_order":["subheading_p3JeNT","heading_KMefdY","text_aVwiWh"],"name":"t:sections.image-with-text.presets.name","settings":{"container":"container","color_schema":"","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/GVM_CHEVY-1500---20260429Stage-3-_-3850-GVM-CHEVY-1500.png","image_width":"50%","image_position":"left","vertical_alignment":"center","column_gap":"medium","row_gap":"medium","padding_left":0,"padding_right":0,"align_content_container":"none","mobile_padding_left":15,"mobile_padding_right":15,"padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":40,"padding_top_mobile":60,"padding_bottom_mobile":60,"show_section_divider":false,"divider_width":"container","custom_id":"","custom_class":"","animations":"inherit"}},"image_with_text_pcJYGC":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"subheading_UXFBYE":{"type":"subheading","settings":{"subheading":"Stage 4: $16,999* - Installed & Engineered"}},"heading_wfcybN":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"<strong>Stage 4: The Heavy Hauler (4250kg GVM + GCM 8750Kg)<\/strong>","highlight_style":"none","enable_highlight_text_color":false,"heading_size":"h2"}},"text_giGN6b":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><em>Maximum legal capacity for the most demanding builds. Ideal for Tray Canopy builds and for the customer who wants to run 35\" Tyres legally.<\/em><\/p><ul><li><strong>GVM Increase:<\/strong> 4250kg (approx. 1672kg payload) upto <strong>GCM Increase<\/strong> rating  8750kg * ZR2 8450kg.<\/li><li><strong>Key Features:<\/strong> Fox 2.5 Performance Elite suspension, ORI 400kg leaf packs, and <strong>required load-rated wheels\/tyres<\/strong>.<\/li><li><strong>Best For:<\/strong> Fully built rigs with rear drawer systems, rooftop tents, and long-range tanks or the ultimate tourer with Tray and Canopies fitted.<\/li><li><strong>Benefit:<\/strong> Massive payload increase that transforms the Silverado into a true heavy-duty platform while retaining 4.5T braking towing capacity.<\/li><li><em><strong>Note: Chevy Silverado ZR2 has reduced GCM due to the 4.2T towing capacity.<\/strong><\/em><\/li><li><strong>Part Number 200kg Leaf Pack: <\/strong>CHV-1500-Stage4-GVM-200<\/li><li><strong>Part Number 400kg Leaf Pack: <\/strong>CHV-1500-Stage4-GVM-400<\/li><\/ul>"}}},"block_order":["subheading_UXFBYE","heading_wfcybN","text_giGN6b"],"name":"t:sections.image-with-text.presets.name","settings":{"container":"container","color_schema":"","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/GVM_CHEVY-1500---20260429Stage-4-_-4250-GVM-CHEVY-1500.png","image_width":"50%","image_position":"right","vertical_alignment":"center","column_gap":"medium","row_gap":"medium","padding_left":0,"padding_right":0,"align_content_container":"none","mobile_padding_left":15,"mobile_padding_right":15,"padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":40,"padding_top_mobile":60,"padding_bottom_mobile":60,"show_section_divider":false,"divider_width":"container","custom_id":"","custom_class":"","animations":"inherit"}},"image_with_text_8GKk7C":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"subheading_drUinH":{"type":"subheading","settings":{"subheading":"Stage 5: $26,999* - Installed & Engineered"}},"heading_FGMkek":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"<strong>Stage 5: The \"No Compromise\" Build (4250kg GVM + GCM 8750Kg)<\/strong>","highlight_style":"none","enable_highlight_text_color":false,"heading_size":"h2"}},"text_AHtUHA":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><em>The pinnacle of Silverado suspension engineering.<\/em><\/p><ul><li><strong>GVM Increase:<\/strong> 4250kg.<\/li><li><strong>Key Features:<\/strong> <strong>Fox 3.0 Internal Bypass Race Series Shocks<\/strong> (front and rear).<\/li><li><strong>Best For:<\/strong> The enthusiast who wants it all—maximum legal payload combined with race-bred suspension technology.<\/li><li><strong>Benefit:<\/strong> The 3.0 Bypass shocks offer unparalleled heat dissipation and damping control. It’s the ultimate \"go-anywhere\" setup that remains legally compliant across Australia.<\/li><li><strong>Part Number 200kg Leaf Pack: <\/strong>CHV-1500-Stage5-GVM-200<\/li><li><strong>Part Number 400kg Leaf Pack: <\/strong>CHV-1500-Stage5-GVM-400<\/li><\/ul><p><em><strong>Note: Chevy Silverado ZR2 has reduced GCM due to the 4.2T towing capacity.<\/strong><\/em><br\/><br\/><\/p>"}}},"block_order":["subheading_drUinH","heading_FGMkek","text_AHtUHA"],"name":"t:sections.image-with-text.presets.name","settings":{"container":"container","color_schema":"","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/GVM_CHEVY-1500---20260429Stage-5-_-4250-GVM-CHEVY-1500.png","image_width":"50%","image_position":"left","vertical_alignment":"center","column_gap":"med